Crepuscle - Draconian Winter  mp3  320k  ak2014 What we got..
Redwood City Melodic Death Metal
Biography
Crepuscle- (pronounced with a soft "sc" like in scent) variant of crepuscule: the time of day immediately following sunset

Crepuscle first came to fruition in the spring of 2006 under the name Draconian Winter. The members during that era, aged 14-18, began writing rudimentary songs while trying to find their sound. The intent was always to write honest metal that they themselves would listen to.
Description
Heavy riffs, enchanting melodies, grand keyboard soundscapes, and varying tempos. We're not afraid to use blast beats or acoustic/clean guitars.
Band Interests
Creating music.
Artists We Also Like
Gemanon, Beautiful Decay, Sea in the Sky, Valensorrow, Viral, Shortfuse. Arsa
